Responsive Portfolio Website
A modern, responsive portfolio website template designed to adapt seamlessly across all devices. This project showcases clean UI/UX design, interactive elements, and optimized layouts for developers, designers, or anyone looking to create a personal online presence.

Features
Responsive Design:

Fully optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.
Includes media queries for smooth layout adjustments.
Interactive Navigation:

Desktop navigation with hover effects.
Hamburger menu for mobile users with animated toggle functionality.
Profile Section:

Displays a central profile image with descriptive text and social media links.
Dynamic Sections:

About: Highlights details in an attractive two-column layout.
Experience: Grid-based articles to showcase skills and achievements.
Projects: Features project images, titles, and interactive buttons.
Contact: Includes styled contact information blocks and a footer section.
Styling and Typography:

Clean and modern design using the "Poppins" font.
Hover animations on buttons, links, and navigation items.
Smooth Scrolling:

Adds a polished user experience with smooth scroll behavior.
Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3 (Flexbox, Media Queries, Transitions)
JavaScript (Toggle functionality for the hamburger menu)
